OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with a little
OL,6,Fdrizzle. Otherwise dry with cloud
OL,7,Fgradually breaking to give some sunny
OL,8,Fperiods this afternoon, although the
OL,9,Feast may remain rather cold and cloudy.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry.
OL,12,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,13,Fwith variable amounts of cloud. Patchy
OL,14,Fmist and frost. Light winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FA dry day with plenty of
OL,17,Fsunshine but eastern Aberdeenshire may
OL,18,Fsee some low cloud at first. Quite
OL,19,Fwarm inland but cooler along the east
OL,20,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
